<section id="about" class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
        About
        <Team />
      </h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-4 py-2 sm:gap-10 lg:col-span-2">
        <p class="text-base text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 sm:text-lg">
          Hello there! I'm a work-at-home dad who finds immense joy in witnessing my kids'
          incredible journey of growth, right from the comfort of our home. My passion for
          technology has been a driving force in my life, and I've channeled that passion into
          empowering small businesses to have engaging websites that truly make a difference. As I
          balance the roles of a dedicated parent and a tech enthusiast, I've discovered that
          there's nothing quite as rewarding as helping businesses thrive in the digital world while
          cherishing every precious moment with my little ones. Life's an incredible adventure, and
          I'm thrilled to be on this unique path, embracing the magic of family and the wonders of
          technology every step of the way.
        </p>
